WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:22.000
ParkAlert runs here as a synthetic local simulation. No Firebase, camera, account, notification, or network request is made.

00:22.000 --> 00:45.000
The QR alias and masked vehicle are repository fixtures, not real owner, plate, location, or QR data.

00:45.000 --> 01:15.000
A reporter chooses a bounded reason, enters a synthetic note, and prepares a local review state.

01:15.000 --> 01:45.000
The preview is explicitly not sent. Direct client alert and scan-log writes remain disabled.

01:45.000 --> 02:15.000
The alert enters a simulated owner inbox and is resolved locally with no external side effect.

02:15.000 --> 02:40.000
Activity entries and simulation controls are local demonstration evidence, not production telemetry.

02:40.000 --> 03:05.000
Firebase rules deployment, App Check, key restrictions, trusted backend controls, and owned-device evidence remain release gates.
